Enemy AI States:

    1. Patrol:
        - Follow patrol route
        - Ocassionally switch routes and go to new areas
    
    (Play notice animation)

    2. Chase:
        - Occurs after AI has detected the player
        - Chase the player until they can no longer be seen

    3. Search:
        - Occurs once the player can no longer be seen
        - Search the area surrounding the player's last known position
